<p>Overlaying preloaded images on canvas is a cheap operation and even stacking 10 sprite sheets on top of each other won't put too much pressure on the cpu in you smartphone. With all the crazy hair styles LPC characters can have with addition of various pieces of equipment and armor we will have hundreds of possible combinations and thus ensuring uniqueness of characters in the game.</p>
